{"tid":1694434,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【文宣升級】移動連濃牆","createTime":"2019-11-05T07:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T08:21:35.000Z","uid":221360,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d20460d60ad225784756f0cc7e613f6c552c301b","tid":1694434,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:15:26.000Z","msg":"近排多左好多green object係連濃牆附近伏手足，d green object真係愈黎愈癲。為左文宣手足安全，大家可唔可以傾下仲有咩有效既方法做文宣？話晒唔係個個人都會上連登同埋入tg group...特別係銀髮族。<br />\n<br />\n我黎一個先：係自己身上貼文宣，例如係自己件衫／背囊到痴返張文宣。<br />\n即係好似咁（fashion呢d野d狗識條鐵咩）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oCKqx6s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoCKqx6s.jpg&h=6b8706e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歡迎比意見。<br />\nbtw我今日見到有手足係背囊到鑲左個pad係出面，大大隻字無限loop黑警d野，搭電梯果陣唔想望佢都會比佢吸引住，呢個方法之前都見到，又ok wor手足。<br />\n冇野阻到香港人架，要繼續進化，繼續升級呀！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">勿忘初心，方得始終<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n不自由，毋寧死。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f73c4132689306f23aac541a7f9058a7436308f8","tid":1694434,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:17:27.000Z","msg":"曱近平"},{"pid":"00ef8e1ab0f6b242c6dce6687eb07037ccf9d4fd","tid":1694434,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:18:10.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"1ee70b0e496bff16b0823bf5d74ff0e9a99efc9c","tid":1694434,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:19:50.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"a795fc9e3525a577a625b84b497422040d44c1b9","tid":1694434,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:20:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攬炒！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒！！再攬炒！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span> <